Customer Purchasing Behavior Analysis

Developed an end-to-end analytics pipeline to understand customer purchasing patterns using MySQL, Python, and Power BI.

Steps:

Create MySQL Database Using Python: Automated the creation of a MySQL database and tables using Python scripts.

Import CSV Data into MySQL: Utilized Python's pandas library to read CSV files and insert the data into MySQL tables.

Connect MySQL to Power BI: Established a connection between MySQL and Power BI using ODBC to import data.

Create Interactive Dashboard in Power BI: Designed and published an interactive Power BI dashboard to visualize customer purchasing behaviors.

This project demonstrates the ability to integrate data from multiple sources and create insightful visualizations to inform business decisions.
